criteria.textblock:
        -  INCLUSION CRITERIA:

               1. The adolescent is between the ages of 15 years 6 months to 17 years 0 month at
                  time of recruitment;

               2. The adolescent lives with the parent or legal guardian at least 50% of the time;

               3. The parent has routine access to the internet and is able to complete on line
                  surveys in English;

               4. A parent or legal guardian agrees to participate.
